      "content": "that seems pretty one-sided to me. you're saying debt reduction is the \"only way,\" but lots of economists argue that investing in people actually grows the economy so much that the debt becomes less of a problem. isn't it also possible that focusing too much on the debt is actually what causes the instability you're worried about?",
